<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CDo you know Sam Bankman-Fried? He see=
ms in over his head and could quickly be in a precarious position,=E2=80=9D=
 Handler wrote in a July 7 email to an unidentified colleague that the bank=
ing executive posted on his personal Twitter account. =E2=80=9COur expertis=
e in rescuing financial services companies might make it worthwhile to meet=
 w him and begin a relationship. Just a thought.=E2=80=9D ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bankman-Fried appears to have ignored the offe=
r. =E2=80=9CHe never responded nor took a meeting,=E2=80=9D Handler posted,=
