ss advice to people looking to develop their careers. =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There followed a tweet listing eight =E2=80=9C=
Conclusions, observations and lessons=E2=80=9D from Handler. The final one:=
 =E2=80=9Carrogance and hubris destroys everything. Every time.=E2=80=9D</p=
>
</blockquote>
